38. It's also important to stay flexible and willing to try different approaches. 
39. If a particular strategy isn't working, don't be afraid to pivot and try something new. 
40. Additionally, it can be helpful to work with a partner or in a group, as this can provide additional perspectives and insights. 
41. As you work through the problem, be sure to document your progress and any insights you gain. 
42. This can help you stay organized and focused, and also make it easier to share your findings with others.
